properties.name: Fun in the Cemetary
properties.description: Posted by Amyflotsom Dead cats, dark clothes, sex between gravestones... Saturday night. Avoiding the cops was the hardest part.

properties.name: Going Very Fast
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomThe 5 freeway going to LA is barren an ugly and very straight. It all lends itself to exceeding the speed limit excessively.

properties.name: Going even faster
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomThe speed limit is around 80 here, so of course, we had to see if we could exceed 100. We did.

properties.name: Great under the stars sex
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomIt was in high school, we were camping out, and we went hiking. Some of us went back, me and a guy stayed behind for a while.

properties.name: High School
properties.description: Posted by Amyflotsom A place of much angst, injury and joy. I began to make money here, and discovered just how hopeless life is. I was not one of the in-crowd.

properties.name: Hot Springs
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomBig signs everywhere warning you that the water can suddenly get very hot (boiling). Other than that, a very lovely place to frolic. We froliced and took pictures of a semi-nude goth girl (me) in the water with steam all around.

properties.name: Humiliation
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI humiliated myself in ways that were so onerous that they must remain secret.

properties.name: I change in to a rabbit
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI was not alone. Someone else was there and also changed.

properties.name: I was born
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI was born here, but quickly left as the hospital administration discovered my parents had no insurance.

properties.name: Interred
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI only get out at night recently.

properties.name: Jail
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI don\'t know anyone that likes jail. Kinda sucks. Especially when I met Lulu, who was like 250 lbs and wanted to sit on me.

properties.name: Kindergarten
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomAn ancient school, with an even more ancient teacher. It was an exciting time though, as my sexuality blossomed and I discovered many new skills such as picking locks.

properties.name: Lost
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI got lost here once, as a small child. It was only for a few minutes, but traumatized me. To this day I am afraid of puffer fish.

properties.name: Lost Lesbian Virginity
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomYea... in a baseball diamond. It was so hot. Unexpected but really satisfying.

properties.name: Lost my virginity
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomLost my virginity in my bedroom. We also did it in my parents room.

properties.name: Loud Dancing
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomThe Tao Beach Club, a nightclub at the Venetian. Loud simple music with a good beat that just vibrates at night. Pillars of fire light the area. Next to a pool which I fell in to. Great times.

properties.name: Moving things around
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI moved many things. Some things I moved from one place to another, and then back again. All for minimum wage.

properties.name: My first real coaster
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomOrland was great, I was still a kid and I loved Universal better than Disney World. My parents had to coax me on to this hulk coaster, I cried all the way but when it was done I wanted to go again... and again...

properties.name: Parents moved away
properties.description: Posted by Amyflotsom Yup. My parents moved without telling me. We were living here at the time. They went back to LA, I stayed in the bay area.

properties.name: Party House
properties.description: Posted by Amyflotsom Not sure if this is the place, but a friend in high school\'s dad was remodeling a house in PV, and she had a key... we would get someone to drive us up there at night was it was the perfect place to party. Isolated, quiet, private. It only lasted thee months but it was cool.

properties.name: Pretty Greeting Girl
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomNo visible means of support.

properties.name: Pretty Greeting Girl
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomCrappy place to work, people were never in a good mood there. I did my best to smile and look pretty but it didn\'t seem to work.

properties.name: Purse stolen
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomHad my tickets and my cell in it. Bad times.

properties.name: Raped
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomDidn\'t get hurt too bad, but worried about disease and crap for some time afterwards.

properties.name: Saw God
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomIt was either god or the pills I took. Not sure which. It was way out in the desert, and there was nothing but dirt and a golf course.

properties.name: Serious Bondage
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomFirst bondage with a girl. Elisa. She was a student at UC Davis. A psych major. At her brother\'s place. I think I must have been tied and gagged in various positions for 3 hours.

properties.name: Shot at
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomJust at the wrong place at the wrong time.

properties.name: Sickest I have ever been
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI don\'t know if it was food or what but I was soooo sick for 2 days. It was in a hotel, and we couldn\'t check out on time. Right next to London Bridge, too.

properties.name: Stabbed
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomI think it was about here. Guy was so strung out on meth. Meth is evil.

properties.name: Stealing an Apple
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomSo I got kicked out of Disneyland for trying to steal the apple from the witch\'s hand in the snow white ride. Turns out they have a camera on it and someone is watching most of the time. They get really upset. So why is it on my Good Places list? Cause Disneyland is still rad, I have a friend that works there, and Bat Day at D-Land is the best!

properties.name: The Mall
properties.description: Posted by Amyflotsom Not really a Good Place per se, but I sure spent enough time here with friends harassing straight people with the simple sight of us and behaving in an unseemly manner. It was fun.

properties.name: Totaled my car
properties.description: Posted by AmyflotsomSome guy made a left turn against a red light and I broadsided him at about 35 mph. Luckily I wasn\'t drunk.

properties.name: Ugly guy sex
